@soumith 

I am sure the code is up-to-date.
First I uninstall the code using the command pip unisntall torch.
Then I remove the old code using the command rm -r pytorch and git clone again.

[pytorch-install-log.txt](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/files/1779720/pytorch-install-log.txt)
